{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782271623648,"sessionID":"ses_108557056ffeZ4F0zj9y2EiqOH","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_snvbhkd9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"gh pr view 64 --json number,title,body,state,isDraft,headRefName,baseRefName,commits,files,additions,deletions,changedFiles","description":"Fetch PR #64 metadata in JSON"},"output":"{\"additions\":15633,\"baseRefName\":\"develop\",\"body\":\"## Summary\\nAdd an automated PR review workflow built around an OpenCode agent, repo config, and a polling script for drafting and optionally submitting GitHub reviews.\\n\\n## How to Test\\n1. Review `pr-review.conf` and update values if needed.\\n2. Run the PR review script against a target PR and verify it creates draft output and worktree state as expected.\\n3. Confirm the OpenCode agent config in `opencode.json` and `.opencode/agents/pr-review.md` matches the intended permission model.\\n\\n## Related Issues\\nNone.\\n\\n## Author Checklist\\n- [x] Code follows team coding standards and style guide\\n- [x] Self-reviewed the code changes\\n- [ ] Added/updated tests for new functionality\\n- [ ] All tests pass locally\\n- [x] Code is properly documented\\n- [x] Synced with latest `develop` branch\\n- [x] PR title follows conventional commit format\\n- [x] Meaningful commit messages used\\n\\n## Additional Notes\\n- Commit was created with `--no-verify` because `scripts/pr-review.py` currently fails the repo's Ruff/docstring/type-annotation hooks.\\n- `.opencode/package-lock.json` is intentionally force-added despite the local ignore rule.\\n\\n## Type of task\\n- [ ] Data Processing\\n- [ ] Model Training\\n- [ ] API Development\\n- [ ] UI Development\\n- [ ] Testing\\n- [x] Debugging\\n- [ ] Refactor\\n- [ ] Performance Improvement / Optimization\\n- [ ] Security\\n- [x] Documentation\\n- [ ] Monitoring\\n- [ ] All\\n\",\"changedFiles\":89,\"commits\":[{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-12T04:20:35Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-12T04:20:35Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(pr-review): add automated PR review tooling\",\"oid\":\"56438a87d95bc60ccdd2534f389fa78df7c4bd81\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-12T04:27:43Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-12T04:27:43Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(pr-review): add usage guide for review script\",\"oid\":\"0dfbddd45182b49c9ddb642f0ce16660baaa51f3\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-12T07:20:15Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"146711676+david-gdp@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCL6kfA\",\"login\":\"david-gdp\",\"name\":\"David Cahyadi\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-12T07:20:15Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(agents): add pr-review, pr-revise, and gh-cli agent skills\",\"oid\":\"f6c011b83afacd4b959af8c7535f211cb3e6b814\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-15T02:52:48Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-15T05:49:10Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Revert parallel PR review processing\",\"oid\":\"cc0232dd6cfcd51035e922fe3875979eff72c070\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-15T03:28:42Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-15T05:49:10Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add parallel PR review processing\",\"oid\":\"2b02bf6d50b985baad120e950fc18032a211b03b\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-15T03:36:24Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":