OCL6kfA\",\"login\":\"david-gdp\",\"name\":\"David Cahyadi\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-22T09:40:00Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Dark-mode mockup with dynamic project sidebar, PR sub-sidebar with\\nstatus icons (reviewing/waiting/needs-action/approved), code diff\\nview, agent review summary panel, and project registration modal.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(auto-review-pr): add agent reviewer UI mockup\",\"oid\":\"d57637d14b9ac081b9792993c5636686681c775a\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-22T09:44:04Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"146711676+david-gdp@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCL6kfA\",\"login\":\"david-gdp\",\"name\":\"David Cahyadi\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-22T09:44:04Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Replace the two-column sidebar (projects + PRs) with a single\\ncollapsible tree sidebar. Projects are section headers with PR counts;\\nPRs nest underneath with status icons. This frees ~280px of horizontal\\nspace for the code diff and review summary panels.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"refactor(auto-review-pr): merge project + PR sidebars into unified tree\",\"oid\":\"1cbc76ed205e8c1fda58ea81938b75b6e2be7d6d\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T02:58:28Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T02:58:28Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(auto-review-pr): add provider boundary refactor plan\",\"oid\":\"06b1b1a891e44fe1fb93e05143f3f1199780af83\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T02:58:36Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T02:59:00Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(auto-review-pr): remove request changes action\",\"oid\":\"6e928a5749321985d2b83056155111e6396af5bc\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T03:03:40Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T03:03:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(auto-review-pr): document provider boundary foldering\",\"oid\":\"8f9ccd9523ba4eca7ccf8bc4f3a545301decbbe9\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T03:32:58Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T03:32:58Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(auto-review-pr): simplify provider boundary plan\",\"oid\":\"b8a44c32c9d2e10766d9d7eb318174706bb3e51f\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T05:25:18Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T05:25:18Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Refactor PR review architecture\",\"oid\":\"dd8c45160e828ea91011005e82b563dd1984e3b6\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T05:40:13Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T05:40:13Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Remove manual single-PR review\",\"oid\":\"c358f379d1db744dcb2956fc72bf5c54ea036677\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T05:59:40Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T05:59:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"- Delete unused run_poll()/run_forever() daemon-mode API\\n- Delete unused extract_feedback()/request_revision() revision helpers\\n- Remove duplicate Backend protocol; use core AgentBackendPort\\n- Trim StreamBus subscribe/unsubscribe/prune listener API\\n- log.py reuses paths.LOGS_DIR instead of recomputing path\\n- Update architecture docs to mark daemon mode as removed\",\"messageHeadline\":\"refactor(auto-review-pr): remove dead code and simplify adapters\",\"oid\":\"f09bcd53e55385db272bde2d1c1ca96e7f5a76e8\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T06:38:21Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T06:38:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"… JSON stdout\\n\\n- Prompt now instructs the model to write the full markdown draft (including\\n  Feedback footer) to <worktree>/.pr-review/pr-<n>-review.md\\n- Pipeline reads the model-written file, moves it to DRAFTS_DIR via\\n  FileDraftStore.adopt(); fails with clear error if file missing or empty\\n- Drop JSON stdout parse path: delete review_output.py, review_schema.py,\\n  parse_structured_review, validate_prompt_review, save_draft wrapper\\n- Drop schema enforcement CLI flags (--output-schema, --json-schema,\\n  --format json, --mode json); prompt-only shaping\\n- Add draft_file field to AgentInvocationRequest\\n- Backends: parse_result returns session_id only (review_text=\\\"\\\");\\n  output_mode renamed to file_write\\n- Add docs/api.md with HTTP API reference\\n- Update tests for the new file-write contract\",\"messageHeadline\":\"refactor(auto-review-pr): model writes draft file directly instead of…\",\"oid\":\"4018e828c60de52855ffd2ae4af2138437d0487b\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T06:47:05Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T06:47:05Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Config loaded once at startup into _config_cache. All endpoints use\\nthe cached config + fresh StateStore (cheap file read). POST /api/review-all\\nrefreshes the cache from disk before running. Eliminates repeated JSON\\nreads + git subprocess calls on every dashboard poll.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"perf(auto-review-pr): cache config, only reload on review-all\",\"oid\":\"6e52d9b74fe336337b4bba54f5f206a8c398009a\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T06:52:24Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T06:52:24Z\",\"messageBody\":\"SSE generator now catches asyncio.CancelledError to break out of the\\nwhile-True loop on shutdown. Add uvicorn timeout_graceful_shutdown=2 so\\nCtrl+C forces exit within 2s instead of waiting forever for open SSE\\nconnections to close.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(auto-review-pr): prevent shutdown freeze on SSE connections\",\"oid\":\"5466194740519dad3917b9c742da7b415a6cbdd3\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T07:16:15Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T07:16:15Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…rite it\\n\\n- Prompt now uses relative path (.pr-review/pr-<n>-review.md) instead of\\n  absolute path, matching the opencode edit permission glob pattern\\n- Remove 'edits' from conflict rules so agent is allowed to write the draft\\n- Update agent description to reflect file-write behavior\\n- Replace dropdown stream selector with tab-based multi-PR stream view on\\n  the main dashboard; auto-connects SSE for active PRs\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(auto-review-pr): use relative draft path in prompt so agent can w…\",\"oid\":\"03915f818d92259ddea71318e2d2979178321e34\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T08:06:26Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T08:06:26Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…ll backends\\n\\n- Remove granular permission rules; allow all tools so agent can write\\n  draft file without hitting deny rules\\n- Restore --format json (opencode), --json (codex), --output-format json\\n  (claude-code), --mode json (pi) so streaming events flow to dashboard\\n- Prompt instructs agent to use built-in edit tool, not bash\\n- Create empty draft file in worktree at setup time so edit tool finds it\\n- syncStreamTabs now creates tabs for reviewing/revision_requested PRs\\n  not just active_prs, so fast-failing reviews still show in the UI\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(auto-review-pr): open agent permissions, restore json format on a…\",\"oid\":\"68b79d2ef3c043d4fe12f106f420f3ec3c8e7c8b\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T08:14:22Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T08:14:22Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Delete notifications.py, notify config field, notifier pipeline hook,\\nnotify_user import, notify test, and dashboard notify config display.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"refactor(auto-review-pr): remove notifications feature\",\"oid\":\"9d88ee833a523df6e631038f5e6cfe4f15866ab9\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T08:18:10Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T08:18:10Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…hors config\\n\\n- Remove editor, skip_draft_prs, skip_bot_authors from Config, ALLOWED_KEYS,\\n  and config parsing\\n- Remove draft/bot skip logic from PrPollingService.detect_changes\\n- Remove is_bot_author helper and is_draft/author_is_bot from\\n  PullRequestSnapshot and gh_cli adapter\\n- Remove corresponding dashboard config display rows\\n- Remove skip-related tests and is_bot_author test\",\"messageHeadline\":\"refactor(auto-review-pr): remove editor, skip_draft_prs, skip_bot_aut…\",\"oid\":\"0a59749704d503dd074ad9dcc37f3d0a0f05ae3c\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-23T11:23:45Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-23T11:23:45Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(auto-review-pr): add SPA review dashboard\",\"oid\":\"327c6361f762af2d7fbe3eb4d537159c00710a7d\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-06-24T01:33:37Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"josephgreffenkomala@mail.ugm.ac.id\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCKZcdg\",\"login\":\"josephgreffenkomala\",\"name\":\"josephgreffenkomala\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-06-24T01:33:37Z\",\"messageBody\":\"- Create .agents/pr-review-agent.md as shared system prompt for all\\n  non-opencode backends\\n- Add agent_prompt field to AgentInvocationRequest\\n- Pipeline reads the shared prompt and writes AGENTS.md into worktree\\n  (codex reads it automatically from cwd)\\n- Codex: add --dangerously-bypass-approvals-and-sandbox for file writes\\n- Claude Code: add --dangerously-skip-permissions + --append-system-prompt\\n- Pi: add --append-system-prompt\\n- Add tests for new flags and agent_prompt passing\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(auto-review-pr): add shared agent config for codex, claude-code, pi\",\"oid\":\"a201986b8f8c946bfb3e2eb1dcb32a411a3da89a\"}],\"deletions\":0,\"files\":[{\"path\":\".coverage\",\"additions\":0,\"deletions\":0,\"changeType\":\"ADDED\"},{\"path\":\".gitignore\",\"additions\":5,\"deletions\":0,\"changeType\":\"MODIFIED\"},{\"path\":\"applications/auto-review-pr/.agents/pr-review-agent.md\",\"additions\":111,\"deletions\":0,\"changeType\":\"ADDED\"},{\"path\":\"applications/auto-review-pr/.agents/skills/gh-cli/SKILL.md\",\"additions\":324,\"deletions\":0,\"changeType\":\"ADDED\"},{\"path\":\"applications/auto-review-pr/.agents/skills/gh-cli/scripts/gh-pr-fmt.sh\",\"additions\":264,\"deletions\":0,\"changeType\":\"ADDED\"},{\"path\":\"applications/auto-review-pr/.agents/skills/pr-review/SKILL.md\",\"additions\":436,\"deletions\":0,\"changeType\":\"ADD